{"sections":{"main":{"type":"page","disabled":true,"settings":{}},"dynamic_rich_text_iMczD9":{"type":"dynamic-rich-text","settings":{"width":"wide","title":"UV Multipacks","text":"<p>UV-reactive body jewelry is perfect for those who love to make a statement, especially under blacklight. At Monster Piercing, our UV multipacks offer a variety of body jewelry pieces that glow in the dark or under UV light, making them ideal for parties, festivals, or anyone looking to add a pop of color to their piercing collection. These multipacks typically include items such as belly bars, tongue bars, plugs, and more, all made from high-quality acrylic or silicone. The vibrant colors and glowing effect make UV jewelry a fun and eye-catching choice for those who want to stand out. Our multipacks provide great value, allowing you to experiment with different styles and colors. Whether you're a fan of bright neon or softer pastel tones, our UV multipacks offer a wide range of options to suit your personal style.<\/p>","heading_size":"medium","text_alignment":"center"}},"1a931267-635a-4600-8852-ca681c8d3614":{"type":"dynamic-collection-list","blocks":{"template--16237148864674__1a931267-635a-4600-8852-ca681c8d3614-collection-1":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"uv-belly-rings","title":""}},"template--16237148864674__1a931267-635a-4600-8852-ca681c8d3614-collection-2":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"uv-flat-backs","title":""}},"template--16237148864674__1a931267-635a-4600-8852-ca681c8d3614-collection-3":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"uv-circular-barbells","title":""}},"template--16237148864674__1a931267-635a-4600-8852-ca681c8d3614-collection-4":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"uv-tongue-bars","title":""}},"template--16237148864674__1a931267-635a-4600-8852-ca681c8d3614-collection-5":{"type":"collection","settings":{"collection":"uv-twisted-barbells","title":""}}},"block_order":["template--16237148864674__1a931267-635a-4600-8852-ca6